name: ILoveYou.vbs
description: Collection: virus.uwu This collection consists a series of 3 pieces, each one is the representation of a computer "virus" (malware) that had a significant impact on the internet. The infection begins when a user receives an email entitled “I Love You” that has a file associated with it called: LOVE-LETTER-FOR-YOU.TXT.vbs This file contains the virus code. I Love You takes all the directions to send a copy of the virus to those people who appear in the infected computer's address book.
